          <title>49ers bring back Robert Saleh as defensive coordinator</title>
          <description><![CDATA[(KRON) -- The San Francisco 49ers will fill their vacant defensive coordinator position with a familiar face. Robert Saleh will return to lead the team's defense after a tenure as the New York Jets' head coach, the 49ers announced Friday. Saleh was the 49ers' defensive coordinator from 2017-2020.]]></description>
